#everyBODYisflawless is a music video featuring American plus-size fashion bloggers and models Gabi Gregg, Nadia Aboulhosn and Tess Munster, lip-synching to Beyonc√©'s 2013 song "Flawless". The video was released on May 7, 2014. It was created by Gregg to promote body positivity and acceptance as a response to the way women are sometimes treated by the fashion community and by internet trolls.


